text: Kokoona sabahana is a species of plant in the family Celastraceae. It is a tree endemic to Borneo where it is confined to Sabah. It is threatened by habitat loss. ==References== sabahana Category:Endemic flora of Borneo Category:Trees of Borneo Category:Flora of Sabah Category:Vulnerable plants Category:Taxonomy articles created by Polbot Category:Plants described in 1994
